OL,3,CJersey headteachers unanimously vote
OL,4,Cagainst introducing bilingual schools
OL,6,FHeadteachers in Jersey have rejected
OL,7,Fthe idea of introducing bilingual
OL,8,Fprimary schools on the island.
OL,10,FIt comes after 24 schools were sent a
OL,11,Fsurvey after a Jersey politician
OL,12,Flodged a proposition to introduce
OL,13,Fphased bilingual teaching in the 2025
OL,14,Fschool year.
OL,16,FHowever, out of the 21 schools that
OL,17,Fresponded, none voted in favour of the
OL,18,Fidea.
