OL,3,CJersey headteachers unanimously vote
OL,4,Cagainst introducing bilingual schools
OL,6,FThe proposition was lodged by Deputy
OL,7,FSir Philip Bailhache who was looking
OL,8,Fto progressively phase the
OL,9,Fintroduction of French-English
OL,10,Fbilingual lessons in three schools,
OL,11,Fbeginning with reception classes.
OL,13,FHe argues it would bring economic,
OL,14,Fpolitical and diplomatic advantages.
