OL,3,CJersey headteachers unanimously vote
OL,4,Cagainst introducing bilingual schools
OL,6,FEchoing this, another headteacher
OL,7,Fsays: "A ridiculous idea. Get the
OL,8,Fcurrent portfolio of school buildings
OL,9,Fup to scratch as they are woefully
OL,10,Finadequate. Ensure the current schools
OL,11,Fare staffed sufficiently with a talent
OL,12,Fpool to draw up, get this done first."
OL,14,FAnother answer reads: "I think there
OL,15,Fare much more important issues in
OL,16,Feducation to consider."
OL,18,FSimilarly, another response says:
OL,19,F"Believe we have more important
OL,20,Fpriorities."
